rest_of_day_open: I think the rest of my week will present challenges at work. I have some assignments to complete that are difficult. Furthermore, I am still dealing with a cold that will make things harder. However, I am looking forward to being able to sleep in this weekend. I am also looking forward to spending time with my family.
critical_positive: What worked well about the conversation is the fact that my partner was more talkative than I am. When I don't know someone well, I prefer to do most of the listening during a conversation. I did find it interesting discussing the differences in our personality traits as well, despite the differences in interests.
critical_negative: What didn't work well was the differences between us. For example, she was a 50-year-old woman from Texas and I am a 27-year-old man from New York. She is in a different place in her life, and also has hobbies that differ from my own. I do think that stalled the ability for the conversation to become deeper than it was.

rest_of_day_open: I see it going just about the same as the previous part of the week. I have had some GI issues since September. I am hoping my recent doctor's visit and the advice I received there will enable my week to proceed with less pain and more physical activities. I hope to spend more time with my goats and my family.
critical_positive: I think we were both articulate and intelligent. We kept things pretty light about the weather at first. We discovered that he lives very close to my parents on the east coast. I enjoyed that he started asking questions about tv watching. I find it difficult to do small talk, so that made it go more smoothly.
critical_negative: I sort of brought up politics. I said something about "please don't hang up if you disagree with my politics." I mentioned watching an interview with Barak Obama. As soon as I said the word politics, his eyes went flat. I think he was afraid I was leading the discussion to a very divisive subject. I never learned his political leanings which was just fine.
employ_7_TEXT: Self employed rancher and freelance writer
